8. [Chemosphere](https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/chemosphere) IF=8.9
9. [Environmental Research](https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/environmental-research) IF=8.4
10. [Ecotoxicology and Environmental Safety](https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/ecotoxicology-and-environmental-safety) IF=7.1
11. [Environmental Research Letters](https://iopscience.iop.org/journal/1748-9326) IF=6.9
12. [Epidemiology](https://journals.lww.com/epidem/pages/default.aspx) IF=4.86
12. [International Journal of Hygiene and Environmental Health](https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/international-journal-of-hygiene-and-environmental-health) IF=7.4
12. [Environmental Health](https://ehjournal.biomedcentral.com/) IF=7.1
12. [Journal of Exposure Science and Environmental Epidemiology](https://www.nature.com/jes/) IF=5.563
